.TH "fairplaytothequeen-by-candela-win32" "6" "2017-04-13" "Fair play to the queen User Manuals" ""
.hy
.SH NAME
.PP
fairplaytothequeen-by-candela-win32 - the command to run Fair play to
the queen.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
fairplaytothequeen-by-candela-win32 [\f[I]options\f[R]]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Fair play to the queen is a demonstration released by Candela in 2005.
fairplaytothequeen-by-candela-win32 is the launcher that use Wine &
PlayOnLinux to run it.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--setdesktop
Set to desktop mode and run (can go in fullscreen)
.TP
--help
Display help for the command
.SH ENVIRONMENT VARIABLEs
.TP
\ APP_RES [widthxheight]
start the app in a widthxheight virtual desktop
.PD 0
.P
.PD
ex.
APP_RES=800x600 fairplaytothequeen-by-candela-win32
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
\f[V]wine\f[R](1)
.SH BUGS
.PP
